text: Sultan Mehmood Chaudhry is a Pakistani politician. He was the Prime Minister of Azad Kashmir between July 1996 to July 2001. In 2021, he became President of Azad Kashmir. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Prime Ministers of Azad Kashmir Category:Presidents of Azad Kashmir
